'''[[black]] [[spot]]'''
#A [[fungus|fungal]] [[disease]] among [[plant]]s, particularly [[rose]]s, that results in black spots on the [[leaf|leaves]].
#A section of [[roadway]] that has been designated as being particularly [[accident-prone]].
#A fictional [[judicial]] device among [[pirate]]s, consisting of a black circle indicating [[condemned|condemnation]].